Tea time with @ladygaga (Lady Gaga) ðŸ«–ðŸŒ·ðŸ”¥

Ahead of the release of the new @jokermovie (â€œJoker: Folie Ã  Deuxâ€), which hits theaters Friday, Lady Gaga sat down for a tea and a talk about her experience playing Harley Quinn and how it inspired her new album, â€œHarlequin.â€

â€œI really love the way that reality and fiction and music and film and pop culture â€” all of these things can have a relationship if we want them to,â€ says Lady Gaga. â€œI think that the way that we told the story in the movie was so surreal, and I think that I want to apply that surrealism to my own music.â€

â€œThis is a special record for me because itâ€™s kind of my celebration of all the masks that Iâ€™ve worn in my career but in one person â€” and allowing it to be an expression of that light,â€ Lady Gaga goes into say. 

Sit down, pour a cuppa and hear more from Lady Gaga about â€œJokerâ€ and â€œHarlequin.â€ ðŸ–¤

â€œThe love I have for breakdancing is indescribable. I love to train consistently because the moves I do require months or even years of practice,â€ says Sanam. â€œThe bigger you think and dream about the sport, the more you will fulfill your dreams. The higher your soul, the more you will grow. 

A few years ago, it was unthinkable to reach such a level in power moves. It was said that girls couldnâ€™t do it. But I told myself I can do it. If I can do it, you can do it too.â€

â€œILLIT is the combination of the phrase â€˜I will,â€™ representing an independent spirit and an adventurous will, and â€˜It,â€™ which stands to symbolize something unique.
 
The message ILLIT delivers with our debut album â€˜SUPER REAL MEâ€™ is that nothing beats a story told from the heart â€” a story about teenagersâ€™ thoughts, emotions and everyday lives. Through our music, we voice our curiosity about the world that surrounds us, our honest feelings and the wilds of our imaginations. We hope to make teenagers feel a sense of kinship, as girls who cherish and find delight in what they are experiencing and feeling at this very moment.â€
